Hong Kong skyline?  No.  Toy display in the Hong Kong airport terminal.  Of course I bought a shiny red taxi!! Fun things to see when you travel.  My trips take me from factory to factory, it’s what I do.  But along the way I do get to see some interesting things too.  Supply chain is not something you capture in a photo, and our clients products are theirs to share, so I share the other interesting things when I can!  #consulting #hk #hongkong #hkairport #asia #asiatravel #businesstravel #travelphotography #supplychainmanagement #supplychain #jewelry #jcsllc #asiajewelry #traveljewelry #ethicalfashion #responsiblesourcing
